:Install Docker from the link below:
  #https://docs.docker.com/get-docker/
:To check whether your docker installation is properly done or not just type in your CLI:
  #(sudo) docker -v
:Run docker in the CLI using commmand:
  #sudo service docker start 
  if it show connection error with daemon then use this link to solve the problem:
   #https://stackoverflow.com/questions/21871479/docker-cant-connect-to-docker-daemon
:Now, simply run type in your CLI:
  (sudo) docker pull the link of the dockerfile in this Repo.
  
